=============================

Recovering grub for a HD Install.

Assuming kanotix installed on sda. 

Boot live install first and:

su
mount /dev/sda1 /mnt
mount --bind /dev /mnt/dev
chroot /mnt
grub-install /dev/sda

now reboot

